## How to attribute this work:

When using or adapting the Build Up / Assess Down framework, please include attribution in one of the following formats:

### Minimal Attribution

```
Build Up, Assess Down framework by Scott Norton
Licensed under CC BY 4.0
```

### Full Attribution

```
Build Up, Assess Down: A Dependency-Based Operating Model for PCI DSS Compliance
by Scott Norton (2025)
Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
[https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
```

### Academic Citation

For academic or professional work, please use the citation formats provided in the [README.md](http://README.md).

